{
  "stem": "16106.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- the thing was-- thing was that they made me the Girl Friday of-- you know, every organization had one SS person, and I was his so-called Girl Friday.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I brought him the coffee, and then the papers, and then the aftershave, and we-- and then we always-- we were [GERMAN], what they called-- surrounded by-- by enemies.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we always were on the move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we were on the move, I was driving this SS as a German lady in a taxi.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We talked about-- with whom?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Depends with whom?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, once I kind-- I kind of-- there was one very nasty guy who took advantage of the Polish girls, and he was saying something to me, and I said, well, [INAUDIBLE] relative, my Herr.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] All right, how do you know those words-- relative?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at one point, they had a discussion about film.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know my [INAUDIBLE] was going, and I had them all fooled, and I was so stupid as I can be, and luckier than anything in the world.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, the luck that I had, you wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I burst out with my favorite film, a film from the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I love that movie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a wonderful actress, and then she somehow-- I don't know how she ends up in the Soviet Union, that-- that land of the free.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she-- she's still afraid of the little black baby will be found out, and then comes the old grandfather, and finds that baby.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she's scared to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Said, darling, he says, you are here in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can have black children, you can have green children, you can even have checkered children.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
